LAGOS  – In a bid to encourage families to travel this Easter season, Aero Contractors is introducing a promo tagged Four For Five (FFF) promo. The airline in a statement said that with this promo, anyone who buys four tickets would automatically get a fifth one for free. The sale of this promotional package, the statement hinted is available for tickets bought on its website and across the counter from March 26 through April 17, 2022. The statement clarified that to be eligible for this promo, booking for all four passengers must be on the same reference. It also advised passengers to make bookings within the window period in order to enjoy the promo. The fifth ticket it said would be valid till the end of June, 2022 from the date of purchase and it could be used at any time within the period. It insisted that the offer was timely for its existing customers and new customers who would have the opportunity to visit or spend time with their loved ones during the holiday season. The statement added: “We are delighted to introduce this promotional package which will assist our customers to re-unite with their loved ones during this Easter holiday season. POLL “At Aero Contractors, we are committed to making flying accessible and making sure our customers have the opportunity to celebrate with their loved ones every holiday.”